<view class="container">
  <image src="http://localhost:5001/images/recipe/04.jpg" class="recipe-image" mode="aspectFill" />
  <view class="recipe-info">
    <text class="recipe-title">红烧羊腱子</text>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">所需食材</text>
      </view>
      <view class="ing-list">
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">葱、姜、蒜</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">花椒</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">干海椒</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">香叶、八角</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">桂皮、茴香</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">干山楂</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">料酒</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">生抽、老抽</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">白糖</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">盐、鸡精</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">香菜</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">胡萝卜等配菜</text></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">烹饪步骤</text>
      </view>
      <view class="step-list">
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>1</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">羊肉洗净切成合适大小，冷水下锅焯水，撇去浮沫后捞出备用。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>2</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">热锅放油，将葱姜切片与八角、香叶等香料下锅煎香。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>3</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">放入羊肉翻炒至均匀变色，加入生抽、老抽、料酒、白糖，加少许水没过肉块。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>4</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">中小火炖约 30 分钟，加入胡萝卜等配菜炖熟，大火收汁，酌情加盐翻拌均匀。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>5</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">出锅撒上香菜即可。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>